  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the investigator new modification for delorme procedure
      in patients with rectal prolapse , assessing intra-operative morbidity and recurrence rate .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In classic delorme operation stripping of the mucosa done and this is associated with
      extensive bleeding in addition to the time consumed in this step.the new modification done by
      the investigator replace this step with another associated with less intraoperative bleeding
      and not time consuming.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
